  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Bear Apartments are self-catered apartments. The well stocked supermarket is just a short walk away from the apartments, all of which have a well equipped kitchen with oven, microwave and stove top.</p>
<p>Optional half board upgrade to the <a data-udi="umb://document/9eb97263e6404b4c8876c7345aeda1d3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9eb97263e6404b4c8876c7345aeda1d3}" title="Crazy Reindeer Hotel">Crazy Reindeer Hotel</a>, including<span> buffet breakfast and dinner (about 350 metres walk). </span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>1</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Bear Apartments are a great addition to our <a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks">Santa Breaks</a> programme. The self-catered apartments are furnished to a high standard, each with their own kitchen, lounge and private sauna. With a central location in Levi, you will be close to all of the resort amenities and Arctic activities.</p>
<h2>Modern and comfortable apartments</h2>
<p>The apartments provide a cosy haven for your Christmas break. The apartments vary in design however the wooden panelling gives them a cosy cabin like feel, and the open plan living space is complete with a kitchen-diner and lounge area - so you'll have space to relax after days spent searching for Santa. Embrace Finnish traditions and enjoy relaxing in your own private sauna included in each apartment. Each of the apartments has room for additional beds, so you'll have enough space for the whole family. </p>
<h2>Cosy Christmas experience </h2>
<p>Celebrate the holiday season in the comfort of your own apartment. T<span>hese cosy apartments are a short distance from</span> the village, where you can find a range of gift shops, cosy cafes and restaurants, as well as a well stocked supermarket. A wintery wonderland awaits you just beyond your front door, explore the wilderness of <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Finnish Lapland</a> on a snowmobile safari, husky safari or snowshoe adventure or Search for Santa at the Elves hideaway. </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
