  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Hiihtäjänkuja 5</strong> is around 63<span>m² sleeping six people in a lower ground duplex style apartment. The entrance to the apartment is on street level, where you have two win bedrooms, WC and an open plan living area with kitchen-lounge area.  Downstairs there is a bathroom with a sauna and two single beds at the bottom of the stairs. These apartments have two toilets and a washing machine. </span></p>
<p><strong>Pikkukarhu 2, 6 &amp; 7</strong> are around 54m² sleeping four people in a one bedroom duplex style apartment. These apartments have a twin bedroom and bathroom with sauna on the upper level. On the lower level there is a double bed or sofa-bed, a cosy kitchen-living area with fireplace and second toilet. These apartments have two balconies.</p>
<p><strong>Pikkukarhu 8</strong> is around 66m² sleeping four people in a two bedroom duplex style apartment. This apartment has a living room, kitchen and twin bedroom with a separate toilet on the lower level. Upstairs there is a second twin bedroom and bathroom with a sauna. This apartment has a balcony on the upper-level.</p>
<p><strong>Karhunvartija Apartments 1 &amp; 6 </strong>are around 65m² sleeping four people in one bedroom duplex style apartment. These apartments have a living room with fireplace, bathroom with a sauna and two single beds in an open area downstairs. On the upper level there is one bedroom, kitchen and WC. These apartments do not have balconies, there is a communal laundry room in the Karhunvartija basement</p>
<p><strong>Karhunvartija Apartment 4 </strong>is around 65m² sleeping four people in one bedroom single level apartment.  This apartment has a twin bedroom with a pergola, and a double sofa bed for two people in the living room. There is an open-plan kitchen and living room with a fireplace and a bathroom with a sauna. There is a communal laundry room in the Karhunvartija basement</p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kitchen with stove, oven, dishwasher, microwave oven, coffee maker, kettle, toaster, fridge and small freezer</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Living area with fireplace (firewood included)</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Radio</li>
<li>Internet (WLAN)</li>
<li>Bathroom with sauna </li>
<li>Drying cabinet</li>
<li>Bed linen and towels</li>
<li>Shared ski room with lockers</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
